41214.name: Percentage of enrolment in primary education in private institutions (%)
41214.description: Total number of students in primary education enrolled in institutions that are not operated by a public authority but controlled and managed, whether for profit or not, by a private body (e.g., non-governmental organisation, religious body, special interest group, foundation or business enterprise), expressed as a percentage of total number of students enrolled in primary education.
